         * FID-008 — which tier is the active source:
         * - `"env"`   = `process.env.OPENROUTER_MASTER_KEY` (tier 1)
         * - `"vault"` = `setup_master_key` save (tier 2)
         * - `"none"`  = no key available; manifest falls back to template
         */
        source: "env" | "vault" | "none";
      };
      
